Speaking after his side's comprehensive 4-1 Champions League quarter-final victory over Roma, via Sport, the French international - who celebrated a goal by showing off his Bar&ccedil;a badge - was questioned over his future at the club, and stated: &quot;My celebration was to say that I love this club. I just want to play, push myself a hundred percent and do well in a club like Bar&ccedil;a.<br />
<br />
&quot;That's what matters to me. The rest are things that come out in the press, true and false. I focus on football.&quot;

